name: 【Lovelive!】Yazawa Nico Charecter LoRA（矢澤·妮可人物模組）
description:
This is a LoRA for generating images of Lovelive character Yazawa Nico.

Making models takes a lot of time and hard work. If you like this LoRA, please click the like button!

V2 Update: Fixed the issue of low-quality generation and added more details.

Recommended weights:

  • Recommended weights: 0.5~0.7

    (Note: If the weight is below 0.4, the LoRA may not work effectively.)

這是一個用於生成Lovelive角色矢澤·妮可的圖像的LoRA

製作模型需要花費很多的時間和精力。如果您喜歡這個LoRA，請幫忙按一個“讚”！

建議權重：

  • 建議權重：0.5〜0.7

    （注意：如果權重低於0.4，則LoRA可能無法生效。）
